Package com.sailthru.mobile.sdk

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MessageActivity
    Activity to display the detail content of a class Message.
    MessageStream
    Class to handle interactions with in-app message stream.
    NotificationBundle
    Wrapper with helpers to load data from the bundle received with a notification sent using Sailthru Mobile Platform
    NotificationCategory
    Defines Notification Categories that can be passed to the SDK to show actions on push notifications.
    NotificationConfig
    Configuration class for building Notifications. These setting will apply to all notifications generated by Sailthru.
    NotificationExtender
    Styles a standard Sailthru Mobile Notification, optionally with a given Message.
    SailthruMobile
    Keeps track of necessary environment variables provided by the developer or google. Also provides the entry point into Sailthru Mobile for the developer to retrieve device information.
